多尔切和加巴纳还利用其展厅举办新书发行活动以及有关其服装的摄影展，如2011年他们的新书《David Gandy》（大卫ˑ甘迪）的发行活动。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.style.it/moda/photogallery/protagonisti-ed-eventi/2011/06/20/dolcegabbana-e-david-gandy.aspx |title=Dolce & Gabbana Celebrates with David Gandy |date=2011-06-20 |author=Carolina Rimondi |publisher=Style.it |accessdate=2012-05-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824052603/http://www.style.it/moda/photogallery/protagonisti-ed-eventi/2011/06/20/dolcegabbana-e-david-gandy.aspx |archivedate=2011-08-24 }}</ref> 当然，他们也利用其它场地，如米兰法理宫（Palazzo della Ragione），他们于2009年5月在此地举办了一场摄影展，展出了从美国版《Vogue》杂志过去90年历史中精选的100余幅图片。此次展览名为''Vogue极致之美（Extreme Beauty in Vogue）''。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.dolcegabbana.com/extreme-beauty-in-vogue/ |title= Extreme Beauty in Vogue |accessdate= 2012-05-19 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120516185919/http://www.dolcegabbana.com/extreme-beauty-in-vogue/ |archivedate= 2012-05-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite article |url=http://www.style.com/peopleparties/parties/scoop/fashionweek-030209_Dolce_Gabbana_Extreme_Beauty/ |title=To the Extreme |accessdate=2012-05-19 |date=2009 |author=Tim Blanks |publisher=Style.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812000232/http://www.style.com/peopleparties/parties/scoop/fashionweek-030209_Dolce_Gabbana_Extreme_Beauty |archive-date=2011-08-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

